</table>
<h3>5.3 管理后台接口</h3>
<h4>5.3.1 后台登录</h4>
<table>
<tr><td>Method</td><td>Path</td><td>Auth</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>POST</code></td><td><code>/admin/auth/login</code></td><td>否</td></tr>
</table>
<p>请求体：</p>
<pre><code>
{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}
</code></pre>
<p>响应：<code>token</code>、<code>user</code>、<code>roles</code>、<code>permissions</code>、<code>menus</code>。</p>
